---
title: Caribbean Jerk Spiced Chicken with Roast Veggie Toss & Lime Mayo
description: Those folks in the Caribbean sure know how to liven up a chicken dish – just add jerk seasoning! We're taking their advice, and including roasted veggies and lime mayo to match the main event.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-jerk-spiced-chicken-ce94d834.jpg
